# .claudeignore - Token Optimization
# Exclude large documentation files to reduce initial token load
# Load these files manually with @.claude/filename.md when needed

# ============================================
# Heavy Strategy Docs (Load on Demand)
# ============================================

# Multi-Tenant SaaS Strategy (~31KB, ~14k tokens)
# Load when: Implementing organizations, RLS, subdomain routing, Stripe
.claude/08-multi-tenant-strategy.md

# Technical Debt Audit (~15KB, ~8.5k tokens)
# Load when: Refactoring, adding tests, error handling improvements
.claude/07-technical-debt.md

# Teaching Style Guide (~10KB, ~6k tokens)
# Load when: Writing documentation, explaining patterns in detail
.claude/09-teaching-style.md

# Appointments Analysis (~21KB, ~11k tokens)
# Load when: Implementing appointments feature specifically
.claude/08-appointments-analysis.md

# Research Files (~17KB, ~10k tokens)
# Load when: Researching UI/UX patterns for AI features
.claude/research-*.md

